young adults refers to the age group '18-25';
potential health concerns are indicated by a family history of diabetes or high blood pressure;
unhealthy eating habits are characterized as consuming junk food occasionally;
normal blood pressure corresponds to a 'normal' bp_level;
regular urination patterns are interpreted as 'not much' urination frequency.

sql:
SELECT DISTINCT n.patient_id
FROM nutrition n
WHERE n.stress = 'high';

